added changes to log_likelihood. still need to work on the optimization of params.
changed B_matrix re_estimation to use gammas like in rabiner. changed the calc model convergance function to return a positive log
changed alphas and betta to be normalized by C_array of alpha sums. changed path selection to be by gammas. changed re-estimation to be like in kemere's paper
changed alpha, betta, gamma and zetta to by trial analysis
